SUMMARY:24 Hours of Lemons Race Weekend at Sonoma Raceway
DESCRIPTION:24 Hours of Lemons at Sonoma Raceway brings wacky race cars\, wild competition\, and nonstop fun to the track March 21–22. Known for its creative themes and budget-built machines\, this fan-favorite endurance race delivers high-energy action and plenty of laughs for drivers and spectators alike.    Don’t miss this unforgettable weekend of grassroots racing excitement.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/24-hours-of-lemons-race-weekend/2026-03-21/
